features: 💙【Unique Design, Solid Structure】This narrow sofa table top shelf is made of three high-quality MDF,and a delicate acquered metal frame, " X " Shape fixed frame makes the storage shelf more stable

💙【Multifunction】The console tables for the entryway can put keys and bags at hand after entering the door. Put it in the small space behind the sofa, light the aromatherapy, lie on the sofa, and pick up a book to read. This sideboard table can also be placed under the TV or as a plant stand in the living room, as a bar table for leisure.

💙【Large storage space】This narrow console table measures: 41.9 x 11.5 x 30.5 inches, just the right size for corner spaces. The 2-tier entry way table with shelves is a further storage space, where shoes or baskets can be placed, making your space look clean and tidy.

💙【Multi-scenario Use】It can be placed in the entryway, hallway, Living Room, Foyer, Corridor, and Office. 4 adjustable footpads are designed for leveling or uneven, protecting your tile and wood floors from scratches
💙【Easy to Assemble】No extra tools needed, It takes about 8 minutes. Clear and detailed instructions, and numbered parts are included in the package to ensure you can easy assembly
body.description: The console table is composed of simple chipboard and metal frame, with simple and unique design, which can be perfectly matched with simple, industrial or modern decoration. It is a perfect choice to put it in the hall or at the entrance, or behind the sofa. Open shelves take up very little space, but can store many things. It is very suitable for storing books, baskets, vases, plants and other small items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact and nice design
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Wimarsbon Sofa Table, a 41.9" entryway table with a metal frame. Here's my review:**Design and Aesthetics (5/5):** The design of the Wimarsbon Sofa Table is modern and sleek. The combination of the metal frame and the narrow wooden top creates a stylish and contemporary look. The simplicity of the design allows it to blend seamlessly with various interior styles.**Sturdiness and Durability (5/5):** The metal frame provides excellent sturdiness to the table. The construction feels solid, and the materials used appear to be durable. The table is well-balanced and capable of supporting decorative items, making it both functional and reliable.**Size and Dimensions (5/5):** The 41.9" size of the sofa table is ideal for entryways or narrow spaces. It strikes a balance between providing a substantial surface area for decor and being compact enough to fit into smaller areas. The dimensions make it versatile for various placement options.**Easy Assembly (5/5):** The assembly process for the Wimarsbon Sofa Table is straightforward. The provided instructions are clear, and all necessary hardware is included. I was able to assemble the table efficiently without any complications.**Versatility (5/5):** This sofa table is versatile in its use. Whether placed in the entryway to catch keys and display decor or utilized behind a sofa to enhance the living room aesthetic, its design allows for diverse applications. The neutral color scheme also makes it easy to pair with different furniture.**Quality of Materials (5/5):** The materials used in both the metal frame and the tabletop seem to be of high quality. The metal is sturdy and well-finished, while the tabletop feels smooth and resilient. The overall quality suggests that the table will withstand regular use.**Functionality (5/5):** The functionality of the sofa table is excellent. It provides a convenient surface for placing items like keys, mail, or decorative pieces. The narrow design allows it to fit into spaces where a larger piece might not be suitable.**Affordability (4.5/5):** Considering the stylish design, sturdiness, size, easy assembly, versatility, and overall quality of materials, the Wimarsbon Sofa Table offers good value for its price. The affordability aligns well with the features and functionality it provides.**Overall Satisfaction (5/5):** My overall satisfaction with the Wimarsbon Sofa Table is high. It meets expectations in terms of design, sturdiness, dimensions, assembly, versatility, material quality, functionality, and affordability. The table enhances the aesthetics of my entryway and proves to be a practical addition to my home.In conclusion, if you're in search of a stylish and functional sofa table for your entryway or living space, the Wimarsbon Sofa Table is a recommended choice. Its modern design, durability, and versatility make it a valuable addition to home decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice entryway table
reviews.reviewText: This decorative entryway table is elegant and looks good with the overall refreshed theme of my home. The table is pretty heavy, but it's also sturdy and feels pretty secure once propped up. This is meant to be covered with decorations anyway, which will hide any, let's say, imperfections that might be present with this. Draping a piece of cloth over it, and putting little knick knacks over it will do it wonders. I'm pretty satisfied with this, and my guests love it too. It's not the best, but it works.
